Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的可以走动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我这么没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经恢复精神了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要落后了
