Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算前方没有路\N我们也要勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到打倒奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换上了全新的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的冒险还没有结束
